  "text": "We employed a three-tiered screening strategy to identify small molecules that preferentially activate the ATF6 UPR transcriptional program for ER PN reprogramming ( Figure 1A) . First, a cell-based HTS was performed using a transcriptional reporter that includes a fragment of the UPR-inducible BiP promoter driving expression of firefly luciferase (ERSE-FLuc; Figure 1B ) [CITATION_1] .",
